## Project conventions — read before editing

Rules live in `{{ ai_folder }}/instructions/`. Start from the README index
in each relevant folder, then load detail files on demand. The instruction
files are authoritative: if this file conflicts, they win.

Index files:

- `general/README.md` (always)
{% if 'python' in languages %}- `python/README.md` (Python)
